title: Santana Best Ballads CD (1996 - Bulgaria) 320k (musicfromrizzo)
description:
I'd suggest you download this CD only as an addition to the great Santana
songs in the download we've just posted for you at this site:
Santana Ultimate Collection 2007 320k-CD(musicfromrizzo)
You'll find great songs on there (2007 CD) that aren't on this 1996 CD such 
as Corazon espinado (lovely lovely music) and Smooth (feat Rob Thomas)
and the supreme "Game of love" (with Michelle Branch)

As for this collection of "Ballads" music, Europa sounds great indeed
and there's also one of my most favourite songs in Instrumental form
by the great Santana - it has a hint of raggae in the first few beats
and then is classic Santana - I do love the song with vocals too
for the most part additionally. gracias Carlos
(En Aranjues Con Tu Amor)

thanks for your seeding support for his dear fans

Michael Rizzo Chessman
